posting_body: ['***SPECIAL: APPLY THE SAME DAY AS YOUR SHOWING AND GET A $500 RENT CREDIT!', '*** CALL TODAY FOR MORE DETAILS!', 'Virginia Terrace Apartments offers 2 bedroom apartment homes in Saint Louis Park, MN.', 'OAK kitchen, white appliances, balcony and much more!', ' Minutes from shopping, Knollwood Mall, dining, recreational opportunities, entertainment and much more!', 'Convenient to Downtown Minneapolis.', 'Call today at', 'show contact info', 'and let our professional staff give you a personal tour of the community.', '$40 Application Fee per Adult', 'Deposit starting at $500', 'Lease Terms: Month-to-Month Rental Agreements with a 9 Month Clause', 'Cats Accepted with the Following Restrictions:', 'Cats - $200 non-refundable pet fee, $15 monthly pet rent, a limit of 2 cats, and must be spayed/neutered.', 'Amenities:', '*Amazing Professional Staff That Understands That Service Counts', '*Expert Maintenance Team with 24-Hour Emergency Assistance Available', '*Heat, Trash, Gas, Water and Sewer Paid', '*Air Conditioning in All Apartments', '*Window Coverings', '*Ceiling Fans', '*Balcony', '*Ample Closet Space', '*Dishwasher', '*Control Access Entries', '*Walking Distance to Elementary and Middle Schools', '*Oak Kitchen', '*Additional Storage', '*Indoor Mailboxes', 'Year Built: 1960', '# of Buildings: 1', 'School District: St. Louis Park', 'Bus Lines: 52, 67', 'Number of Floors: 3', 'Parking: Off-Street Parking', 'Garages: None', 'Laundry:', 'On-site, First Floor- Coin Operated', 'Cable TV: Cable --Internet Ready', '*Prices and availability are subject to change at any time.']
